{"tid":20540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長沙市售廉價合成肉　雞鴨肉加香精充當牛肉","createTime":"2016-12-03T11:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T17:04:02.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b7b8d7c3b4a954e158b5e54a4389a418166c5e0","tid":20540,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bkncn-20161203141332676-1203_05011_001_01p.jpg?20161203153524\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161203141332676-1203_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161203153524&h=ebb423ca&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n吃火鍋時必備的肥牛及羊肉，竟也有假！湖南長沙市面上最近出現一些平價火鍋「牛肉」及「羊肉」，被揭其實是用其他動物的肉，再加上香精及澱粉混合而成的「合成肉」。這些合成肉的售價比真正的牛羊卷便宜超過一倍，並已大量流入當地多間食肆。 <br />\n<br />\n當地記者走訪長沙多個菜市場，發現牛肉的均價約為35元40元（人民幣．下同）；惟當地一間冷凍食品公司，所出售的袋裝肥牛卷，卻只需15元，分量相約，但價格卻差近一倍。對於這些平價「牛、羊肉卷」的來源，冷凍食品店員一時表示是做豬肉做的，一時又指是雞鴨肉做的，並加入澱粉及香精。 <br />\n<br />\n據業內知情人士表示，市面上低於30元一斤的牛肉都並非真牛肉。此外，專家表示，真牛肉的紋理較為粗糙，而且煮熟後不會散開；合成肉紋理較為細膩，煮熟後會散開。 <br />\n<br />\n及後，長沙市雨花區監督管理局高橋食藥監所展開執法行動，冷凍食品公司負責人當場承認所售賣的牛羊肉，均由其他動物的肉合成加工而成。執法人員隨後對多間食品公司開出責令改正通知書，對於貨品來源，正在進一步調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bkncn-20161203141332676-1203_05011_001_02b.jpg?20161203153524\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161203141332676-1203_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20161203153524&h=5f4edf47&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n專家指合成肉的紋理較細膩，真牛肉紋理較為粗糙。（電視畫面）"},{"pid":"8064cd7bb809b9ee97350f934eb59911fed8cf2d","tid":20540,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb9ac1c73b7df1114b82ccbea76719bf5f1c434","tid":20540,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81fc6f5f9156e11b41a4ae7f4f4b6aa3953aa99","tid":20540,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a28effbbad3969fcc28ab6bcd943b27eb9e9e3","tid":20540,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"屌，支那咁多人，幾時有人肉充豬肉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123c9d7ad3f4de8510f70ed15e771f8e6dbd6471","tid":20540,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，支那咁多人，幾時有人肉充豬肉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能食緊唔知姐"},{"pid":"9a5f28ec73b0cdf53d6506f22d4d86c697dc9292","tid":20540,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"次次返大陸都淨係食菜, 雖然都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b615b1348fbeb15f20ca6ece1e72c02583710a","tid":20540,"uid":35651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:05:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f3bc883d163203a0aa25890163c683055608375","tid":20540,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:08:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌，支那咁多人，幾時有人肉充豬肉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能食緊唔知姐</blockquote><br />\n家明呀&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673004a04a2042cb14b0c564020ec031116f620c","tid":20540,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌，支那咁多人，幾時有人肉充豬肉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能食緊唔知姐</blockquote><br />\n唔喺咁大鑊麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hk